{"tid":2284750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉頴匡：泛民辭得太遲惹人笑柄 但有做比無做好","createTime":"2020-11-13T14:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T08:52:01.000Z","uid":273675,"like":92,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"33fddee3a87185d2b47fcf2722c4bfdd8511a770","tid":2284750,"uid":273675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3FwVsuj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3FwVsuj.png&h=c444e8b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkdinterview/posts/402884824426231\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkdinterview%2Fposts%2F402884824426231&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIp1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=ee659725\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkdinterview/posts/402884824426231</a><br />\n泛民及本土抗爭派於立法會年度開始前曾就是否留任立一事意見分歧。本土抗爭派認為民主陣營議員應「拒絕委任」；而泛民議員則認為應該堅持議會戰線。經過參考民調後決定留守議會的十九位泛民議員，近日因四名議員被褫奪議員資格而集體辭去議席。￼￼<br />\n<br />\n本土抗爭派的劉頴匡認為非法延任議會、政權的不合理DQ已非新鮮事，若然是要以總辭去表態、體現齊上齊落，那一早便應該集體總辭。￼￼他又指縱然辭職來得太遲，￼但亦較繼續留任議會好；藉著這個機會，￼希望民主派能感受到本土派一直所受到的打壓，未來應共同探討如何在議會外推動抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n#泛民總辭 #立法會 ￼￼￼￼￼#民主派 #劉頴匡 #本土抗爭派"},{"pid":"192673fa23ecd6ce327920f722bc70db477276a8","tid":2284750,"uid":273675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7b59ff2e8622a9fe5035b5bbd0514f1125a5df","tid":2284750,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:27:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6237835ea49dbd1c6b3d5f982a9106080c22aa89","tid":2284750,"uid":243677,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:29:38.000Z","msg":"冇錯 泛民既做法係唔完美 但屌完後麻煩槍口一致對外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces